{"tid":1980701,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"實體遊戲時代終結！capcom宣佈數位遊戲已佔比例7成","createTime":"2020-04-20T08:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T00:26:32.000Z","uid":56731,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"5635414b364d7d4515e7f75a5df0ddee09f4888e","tid":1980701,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"眾所周知遊戲界既兩大龍頭近年都主力推數位遊戲<br />\n個個月都搞特價日日都sales gamepass<br />\n依個世代將所有主力ip注力係遊戲界主力平台既capcom都受到影響<br />\n正式宣布佢哋數位版已經過7成<br />\n最近日本唔少收集實體軟銷既平台都冇再做，睇黎睇實銷排行去論一款遊戲賣唔賣得既時代正式終結<br />\n<br />\n『バイオハザード RE:2』『モンスターハンターワールド：アイスボーン』とヒットが続くカプコン。2020年9月4日にはハリウッドで製作された実写映画も日米で同時公開される。ゲームで蓄積したユーザーデータを連動させ、マーケティングの相乗効果を狙うという同社の辻本春弘社長に話を聞いた。<br />\n<a href=\"https://xtrend.nikkei.com/atcl/contents/18/00294/00008/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxtrend.nikkei.com%2Fatcl%2Fcontents%2F18%2F00294%2F00008%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=487d3030\" target=\"_blank\">https://xtrend.nikkei.com/atcl/contents/18/00294/00008/</a>"},{"pid":"70ff902acc4c760a7af6bbbe568573b3b07cb79a","tid":1980701,"uid":25794,"like":65,"dislike":6,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"如果唔係貪賣返出去果一百幾十<br />\n數位版幫屋企慳唔少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b955903dd5e8124be78cabf2430e1f5cc1aa04f","tid":1980701,"uid":22288,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7da61353e607be0288e6ab5d6ad18a81ac0c7466","tid":1980701,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"70ff902acc4c760a7af6bbbe568573b3b07cb79a","tid":1980701,"uid":25794,"like":65,"dislike":6,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"如果唔係貪賣返出去果一百幾十<br />\n數位版幫屋企慳唔少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci